<div class="column span-8">
  <h1>Community</h1>
  <p>Stay informed about the latest web services and happenings in NREL's developer network.</p>

  <h2><%= link_to("Follow Us on Twitter", "http://twitter.com/NRELdev") %></h2>
  <p>Find us on Twitter <%= link_to("@NRELdev", "http://twitter.com/NRELdev") %> where we'll announce new APIs or any API changes.</p>

  <h2>Get Started</h2>
  <p>Still waiting to build something great? Explore our <%= link_to("available services", doc_path) %> and <%= link_to("get your own API key", signup_path) %>.</p>
  <p>Questions, comments, or feel like sharing? Reach out to us <%= link_to("@NRELdev", "http://twitter.com/NRELdev") %> or <%= link_to("contact us directly", contact_path) %>.</p>
</div>

<div class="column span-4 last">
  <script src="http://widgets.twimg.com/j/2/widget.js"></script>
  <script>
  new TWTR.Widget({
    version: 2,
    type: 'profile',
    rpp: 4,
    interval: 6000,
    width: 'auto',
    height: 300,
    theme: {
      shell: {
        background: '#1875be',
        color: '#fff'
      },
      tweets: {
        background: '#ffffff',
        color: '#444444',
        links: '#004f99'
      }
    },
    features: {
      scrollbar: false,
      loop: false,
      live: false,
      hashtags: true,
      timestamp: true,
      avatars: false,
      behavior: 'all'
    }
  }).render().setUser('twitterapi').start();
  </script>
</div>
